This is an automatic deception detection method for "INeural mechanisms for explaining individual variability of deception in a naturalistic situation"

Author: Xiaoling Zhang; Meiyan Huang @Southern Medical University

This repository contains the following files:

Main.py: Model training.
Model.py: Code for automatic detection method based on fNIRS_T.
Readdata.py: Load the specified dataset.
CAM.py: Code for calculating the Grad-CAM based on Channel.
Cal_performance.py: Calculate the performance of method.
Please contact Meiyan Huang (huangmeiyan16@163.com) or Xiaoling Zhang (zhangxiaoling9911@163.com) for any comments or questions.

